act.article:
2 Definitions.—In 
these rules, unless the context otherwise requires—


         a  ‘Act’ means 
the Dock Workers (Regulation of Employment) Act, 1948 (9 of 1948); 


         b ‘Chairman’ 
means the Chairman of the Dock Workers Advisory Committee;


         c  ‘Committee’ 
means the Dock Workers Advisory Committee;


         d  ‘Member’ 
means a member of the Dock Workers Advisory Committee.
